[signal arg="lockmovement"]
Woman: You- You monsters!
join Paul center
Paul: What was that for?
Woman: I know what you did, we all do!  You killed our god!
Paul: H- How do you know that?
Woman: Our power's out!  How else would that be?!
join Narrator center
Narrator: Paul looks down defeated
Woman: We will let you pass, we cannot stop you, but do not stay.
Narrator: The kids pass through the town
[signal arg="allowmovement"]
[signal arg="changescene7"]